{"word":"καταργέω","slug":"καταργέω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ϰαταργέω</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:κατά\">κατά</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀργέω\">ἀργέω</a></el>; ‘cause to be idle’] ‘cause to become ineffective/inoperative’, in various aspects<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp> make unproductive <a href='B:490 13:7'>Lk 13:7</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp> make ineffective, nullify, terminate <a href='B:520 3:3'>Ro 3:3</a>, <a href='B:520 3:31'>31</a>; <a href='B:520 4:14'>4:14</a>; <a href='B:520 6:6'>6:6</a>; <a href='B:530 1:28'>1 Cor 1:28</a>; <a href='B:530 2:6'>2:6</a></b> (the point being that the leaders are in effect made jobless; <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ sim.\">sim.</a> <b><a href='B:530 15:24'>15:24</a></b>); <b><a href='B:550 3:17'>Gal 3:17</a>; <a href='B:560 2:15'>Eph 2:15</a>; <a href='B:600 2:8'>2 Th 2:8</a>; <a href='B:620 1:10'>2 Ti 1:10</a>; <a href='B:650 2:14'>Hb 2:14</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἀπό\">ἀπό</a></el><b> <a href='B:520 7:2'>Ro 7:2</a>, <a href='B:520 7:6'>6</a>; <a href='B:550 5:4'>Gal 5:4</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>c.</pp> abolish, eliminate <a href='B:530 6:13'>1 Cor 6:13</a>; <a href='B:530 13:8'>13:8</a>,</b> <b>10f; <a href='B:530 15:26'>15:26</a>; <a href='B:540 3:7'>2 Cor 3:7</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:καταράομαι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:καταριθμέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}